{"tid":884743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休警涉偷29元耳機　官指有悔意判罰2000元","createTime":"2018-11-01T00:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T05:30:42.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"dd012fef9cc415c1c1a6cfff8d059ccf767a14d3","tid":884743,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181031/_2018103111010191060.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181031%2F_2018103111010191060.jpeg&h=29da9801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告張志良。<br />\n<br />\n上月退休的54歲男警員，去年底在深水埗一間店舖內，涉嫌盜竊一對價值29港元的耳機，店員發現後報警將他拘捕。男警今於西九龍法院承認一項盜竊罪，他於認罪後一直將手放在左胸上。暫委裁判官余俊翔表示考慮到被告盜竊金額低，為同類案件中較輕，犯案前一直有正面品格，以及他肯坦承錯誤，見有悔意，故判罰款2000元。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告張志良於去年12月21日晚上7時許，在深水埗一間電子特賣城內，先後採購了兩條手機充電線發耳機，但卻將白色耳機收在自己右後褲袋中，而付款時亦只支付了充電線之金額。稍後張試用充電線時，被店員截停後發現偷取耳機於是報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師求情時指，張於1987年入學堂後一直於北區水警總部任職水警，有次為了追截非法入境者而滾下山，因而腰部受傷，被調往報案室任文職。自此後張覺自己無用，人生失意，直到母親有腦瘤，妹妹亦相繼患上乳癌，才驚覺自己有情緒困擾。向警方心理服務科求助後，被診斷出有焦慮、抑鬱及自殺傾向，亦曾入院兩個月。辯方律師續指張之前一直奉公守法，已深感後悔，望可輕判。<br />\n<br />\n余官判刑後勉勵被告54歲仍然年輕，即使過去不如意，仍然可以努力積極地由低谷走出來，只要他願意接受他人幫助，未來仍可以很精彩，望他可接受自己過失，向前方生活前進。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：陳楚琨<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1353093/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1353093%2F&d=Vkq%2BgCISrp03aRl07zadepWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=910ec9cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1353093%2F&h=7b47755d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1353093/</a>"},{"pid":"e0ef3346e17568cb746a73fe2d31626000275fc4","tid":884743,"uid":4942,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:23:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n偷嘢犯法就要坐監啦<br />\n<br />\n仲要警察知法犯法  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54b0e99c2af1f1a8b991c6a0b64f8e93632b759","tid":884743,"uid":2471,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"要返工 不了"},{"pid":"fa10ce383efdf5771fa7b39afd39126cc8d8be26","tid":884743,"uid":123587,"like":15,"dislike":12,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e0ef3346e17568cb746a73fe2d31626000275fc4","tid":884743,"uid":4942,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:23:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n偷嘢犯法就要坐監啦<br />\n<br />\n仲要警察知法犯法  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:24:55.000Z","msg":"偷嘢唔一定坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b746ec9ac39559c6968f286300f3aba8e48d6da7","tid":884743,"uid":31237,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"呀sir偷野唔使你教"},{"pid":"d2ca677e8bb4f9a7856951a6cb1e04ea3e13db1f","tid":884743,"uid":92376,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:28:40.000Z","msg":"阿蛇罰錢唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd43f9f8e8ca0e66df259a3c987f7cb68204d19","tid":884743,"uid":137506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"唔係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a57831b75cfce8a6e21a74d392cf62f393a261","tid":884743,"uid":108347,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"悔佢老味意，豬sir個啲唔見個官話冇悔意重判，富二代7次非禮又有悔意輕判<br />\n<br />\n屌那星根本就搵藉口重判普通人輕判有錢佬/自己友"},{"pid":"2a779f8c2110a55cef1610d918505090e8d78bdb","tid":884743,"uid":40606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd012fef9cc415c1c1a6cfff8d059ccf767a14d3","tid":884743,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:20